metadata.name: Wheels
metadata.display_title: Remove commented out build dependency on oldest-supported-numpy

head_commit.message:
Remove commented out build dependency on oldest-supported-numpy

python-blosc2 >= 2.2.6 depends on a version of NumPy (>= 1.20.3) which is
above that which oldest-supported-numpy depends on (1.17.3) (at least for
Python >= 3.8).

repository.name: PyTables
repository.description: A Python package to manage extremely large amounts of data

steps.code:
mkdir hdf5_build
if [[ Linux = 'Linux' ]]; then
  docker run --rm -e HDF5_DIR=/io/hdf5_build -e CFLAGS=-g0 -e HDF5_VERSION=1.14.1-2 -v `pwd`:/io:rw quay.io/pypa/manylinux2014_x86_64 /io/ci/github/get_hdf5.sh
else
  HDF5_DIR=`pwd`/hdf5_build ci/github/get_hdf5.sh
fi

steps.code:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install libbz2-dev libhdf5-serial-dev liblzo2-dev
sudo apt install latexmk texlive-fonts-recommended texlive-latex-recommended texlive-latex-extra texlive-plain-generic

python -m pip install --upgrade setuptools pip wheel build
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m pip install sphinx>=1.1 sphinx_rtd_theme numpydoc ipython
python -m pip install "blosc2>=2.2.6"

mkdir hdf5_build
if [[ Linux = 'Linux' ]]; then
  docker run --rm -e HDF5_DIR=/io/hdf5_build -e CFLAGS=-g0 -e HDF5_VERSION=1.14.1-2 -v `pwd`:/io:rw quay.io/pypa/manylinux2014_aarch64 /io/ci/github/get_hdf5.sh
else
  HDF5_DIR=`pwd`/hdf5_build ci/github/get_hdf5.sh
fi
